hing is in smaller print and located near the top of the page. Links to other databases from the same company are often close by.\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div> <!-- swiffy -->\r\n\r\n  <h5 style=\"margin-top:8px\">Understanding the Differences</h5>\r\n\r\n  <p>Be sure you know the difference between the <strong>database name</strong> and the <strong>database provider</strong> that hosts the database. For example, EBSCOhost is the name of the database provider that hosts Academic Search Complete but it also provides access to many other databases.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"vert_hottip\" style=\"position:float;top:130px;\">\r\n  <div class=\"swiffy\">\r\n    <iframe src=\"/swiffy/Advanced_p10.html\" style=\"width:350px;height:375px;border:0;\"></iframe>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"end\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"page_nav\">\r\n  <a href=\"advanced_search_9\" class=\"arrow_back\">Back</a>\r\n  <div class=\"page_numbers\">10 of 15</div>\r\n  <a href=\"advanced_search_11\" class=\"arrow_forward\">Forward</a>\r\n</div>','<h6>Different  Databases = Different Information</h6>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width:440px\">\r\n\r\n  <p>Different databases search different sources and types  of information. Match the type of information you need to the database you choose.</p>','Imported with node_import.',1353520085,2),(147,536,1,'Self-Check','\n\n<h6>Self-Check</h6>\n\n<div class=\"swiffy\">\n  <iframe src=\"/swiffy/Advanced_p9.html\" style=\"width:775px;height:375px;border:0;\"></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"end\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"page_nav\">\n  <a href=\"advanced_search_8\" class=\"arrow_back\">Back</a>\n  <div class=\"page_numbers\">9 of 15</div>\n  <a href=\"advanced_search_10\" class=\"arrow_forward\">Forward</a>\n</div>','\n\n<h6>Self-Check</h6>\n\n<div class=\"swiffy\">\n  <iframe src=\"/swiffy/Advanced_p9.html\" style=\"width:775px;height:375px;border:0;\"></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"end\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"page_nav\">\n  <a href=\