th:380px; float:left;\">\r\n\r\n  <h4>How Do I Find Articles?</h4>\r\n\r\n  <p>Whether you need a scholarly article or an article from a newspaper or popular magazine, the University of California libraries have hundreds of databases in all different subject areas to help you.</p>\r\n\r\n  <p>With so many to choose from, it can all seem a bit confusing, but don&rsquo;t worry.&nbsp; You will be more confident by the end of this lesson because you will know:</p>','Imported with node_import.',1353521669,2),(171,560,1,'How Do I Do a Subject Search in My Catalog? Step #1','\n\n<h3>How Do I Do a Subject Search in My Catalog? Step #1</h3>\n\n<p>Once you&rsquo;ve found a book closely related to your topic, you can use the book&rsquo;s subject headings to help you find additional resources on the same topic.  Click on a title you like to see more information.</p>\n\n<div class=\"image\">\n  <img src=\"images/content/books_p13.jpg\" width=\"794\" height=\"231\" alt=\"search result\" />\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"end\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"page_nav\">\n  <a href=\"books_12\" class=\"arrow_back\">Back</a>\n  <div class=\"page_numbers\">13 of 15</div>\n  <a href=\"books_14\" class=\"arrow_forward\">Forward</a>\n</div>','\n\n<h3>How Do I Do a Subject Search in My Catalog? Step #1</h3>\n\n<p>Once you&rsquo;ve found a book closely related to your topic, you can use the book&rsquo;s subject headings to help you find additional resources on the same topic.  Click on a title you like to see more information.</p>\n\n<div class=\"image\">\n  <img src=\"images/content/books_p13.jpg\" width=\"794\" height=\"231\" alt=\"search result\" />\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"end\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"page_nav\">\n  <a href=\"books_12\" class=\"arrow_back\">Back</a>\n  <div class=\"page_numbers\">13 of 15</div>\n  <a href=\"books_14\" class=\"arrow_forward\">Forward</a>\n</div>','Imported with node_import.',1349392341,2),(172,561,1,'How Do I Find Books on the Same Topic?','<div style=\"width:690px