 catalog.</p>','Imported with node_import.',1353528068,2),(173,562,0,'Why Do I Need a Call Number?','<h3>Why Do I Need a Call Number?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The <strong>call number</strong> is the book’s address in a library. Follow these steps to find a book on the shelf:</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width:380px; float:left\">\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li>Find the library name and location (often listed as &ldquo;Location&rdquo;).</li>\r\n    <li>Use the library and campus map to locate the library building. </li>\r\n    <li>When you get to the correct library building, check posted directories for call number locations. </li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width:400px; padding-top:6px; float:right\">\r\n<!--[if gte IE 9]>\r\n  <style type=\"text/css\">\r\n    .gradient {\r\n       filter: none;\r\n    }\r\n  </style>\r\n<![endif]-->\r\n<div class=\"swiffy\">\r\n<div id=\"hottip\" class=\"horizontal gradient\">\r\n	<div id=\"ht_icon\">\r\n		<div id=\"ht_title\">Hot Tip</div>\r\n		<div id=\"ht_ro_text\">Roll over me.</div>\r\n	</div>	\r\n	<div id=\"ht_content\">\r\n		Call numbers are arranged in alpha-numeric order. The call number is based on the book\'s subject, author\'s last name, and publication date.\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div> <!-- swiffy -->\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width:800px; float:left\">\r\n <p><em>Try it out. Place the call numbers on the books in the correct order, left to right.</em></p>\r\n  <div class=\"swiffy\">\r\n    <!-- iframe src=\"/swiffy/Books_p11.html\" style=\"width:700px;height:300px;border:0;\"></iframe -->\r\n<div class=\"flash\" align=\"center\">\r\n      <object id=\"FlashID\" classid=\"clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000\" width=\"700\" height=\"300\" style=\"visibility: visible; \">\r\n              <param name=\"movie\" value=\"swf/Books_p11.swf\">\r\n              <param name=\"quality\" value=\"high\">\r\n              <param name=\"wmode\" value=\"opaque\">\r\n              <param name=\"swfversion\" value=\"9.0.45.0\">\r\n